+semantic HTML
+
+optimized heading hierarchy
+
+metadata
+
+OpenGraph tags
+
+Twitter cards
+
+XML sitemap
+
+robots.txt
+
+schema markup
+
+image optimization
+
+lazy loading
+
+fast page speed
+
+
