+
+Style
+
+Blend:
+
+botanical illustration
+
+premium organic branding
+
+ecological storytelling
+
+modern ecommerce UI
+
+
+Avoid:
+
+overly corporate design
+
+neon startup aesthetics
+
+sterile minimalism
+
+
+
+---
+
+14. UI Style
+
+Use:
+
+rounded cards
+
+soft shadows
+
+organic shapes
+
+earthy gradients
+
+subtle animations
+
+nature-inspired textures
+
+
+
+---
+
+15. Homepage Hero
+
+Suggested Hero Text
+
+Option 1
+
+“Grow the Extraordinary.”
+
