+Nayab Seeds — Refined Product Requirements Document (PRD)
+
+Shopify-Powered Ecological Seed Store
+
+Brand: Nayab Seeds
+Tagline: Grow the Extraordinary
+
+
+---
+
+1. Project Vision
+
+Build a clean, premium, modern ecological seed ecommerce website for Nayab Seeds using:
+
+Shopify backend
+
+Lovable frontend generation
+
+React + Tailwind architecture
+
+SEO-first structure
+
+
+The first version should focus on:
+
+making the store functional
+
+selling seeds
+
+educational gardening content
+
+mobile optimization
+
+strong branding
+
+scalability
+
+
+Do NOT build advanced AI systems yet.
+
+Future-ready placeholders should only exist for:
+
+Forum/community features
+
+Native Karachi ecological project integration
+
+Plant quiz functionality
+
+
+
+---
+
+2. Brand Identity
+
+Nayab Seeds should feel:
+
+botanical
+
+trustworthy
+
+earthy
+
+educational
+
+premium
+
+hopeful
+
+ecological
+
+community-oriented
+
+
+Inspired by:
+
+seed preservation
+
+biodiversity
+
+urban gardening
+
+ecological restoration
+
+Pakistani gardening culture
+
+
+
+---
+
+3. Logo Usage
+
+Use the uploaded Nayab Seeds logos for:
+
+navbar branding
+
+favicon
+
+footer branding
+
+loading screen
+
+packaging inspiration
+
+social sharing previews
+
+
+
+---
+
+4. Color Palette
+
+Derived from uploaded logo:
+
+Primary Colors
+
+Deep Forest Green — #1F4D36
+
+Botanical Green — #4F7D4F
+
+Earth Brown — #7A4E2D
+
+Warm Gold — #D4A62A
+
+Soft Cream — #F6F2E8
+
+
+
+---
+
+5. Typography
+
+Headings
+
+Cormorant Garamond OR
+
+Playfair Display
+
+
+Body
+
+Inter OR
+
+Source Sans Pro
+
+
+Typography should feel:
+
+elegant
+
+readable
+
+nature-inspired
+
+premium
+
+
+
+---
+
+6. Technical Stack
+
+Frontend
+
+React
+
+TailwindCSS
+
+Framer Motion
+
+Lovable-compatible structure
+
+
+Backend
+
+Shopify
+
+Shopify Storefront API
+
+Shopify CMS
+
+
+Hosting
+
+Vercel preferred OR
+
+Netlify
+
+
+
+---
+
+7. Main Website Goals
+
+The website must:
+
+sell seeds online
+
+be easy to manage
+
+load fast
+
+rank on Google
+
+be AI-search friendly
+
+educate customers
+
+support future expansion
+
+
+
+---
+
+8. Website Structure
+
+Pages Required
+
+Home Page
+
+Sections:
+
+1. Hero Section
+
+
+2. Featured Seeds
+
+
+3. Categories
+
+
+4. Ecological Mission
+
+
+5. Beginner Gardening Section
+
+
+6. Testimonials
+
+
+7. Blog Preview
+
+
+8. Newsletter Signup
+
+
+9. Footer
+
+
+
+
+---
+
+Shop Page
+
+Features:
+
+category filtering
+
+product search
+
+sorting
+
+Shopify sync
+
+responsive grid layout
+
+
+Categories:
+
+Vegetables
+
+Flowers
+
+Herbs
+
+Native Plants
+
+Rare Seeds
+
+Fruit Seeds
+
+Tree Seeds
+
+Beginner-Friendly Plants
+
+
+
+---
+
+Product Pages
+
+Each product page should include:
+
+title
+
+price
+
+stock status
+
+growing difficulty
+
+watering needs
+
+sunlight requirements
+
+germination time
+
+climate compatibility
+
+Karachi growing suitability
+
+planting instructions
+
+related products
+
+
+Features:
+
+image gallery
+
+zoom
+
+add to cart
+
+wishlist
+
+mobile optimization
+
+
+
+---
+
+About Page
+
+Should communicate:
+
+Nayab Seeds mission
+
+ecological values
+
+biodiversity awareness
+
+gardening accessibility
+
+restoration mindset
+
+
+Tone:
+
+warm
+
+personal
+
+trustworthy
+
+
+
+---
+
+Blog / Learning Hub
+
+Important for SEO and brand authority.
+
+Topics:
+
+gardening guides
+
+Karachi planting tips
+
+balcony gardening
+
+composting
+
+native plants
+
+beginner gardening
+
+pollinator gardening
+
+seasonal planting
+
+
+Features:
+
+categories
+
+tags
+
+SEO optimization
+
+internal linking
+
+article previews
+
+
+
+---
+
+Contact Page
+
+Include:
+
+contact form
+
+WhatsApp button
+
+Instagram link
+
+FAQ
+
+shipping policy
+
+return policy
+
+
+
+---
+
+9. Ecommerce Features
+
+Required
+
+Shopify cart
+
+checkout
+
+inventory sync
+
+customer accounts
+
+order tracking
+
+discount codes
+
+wishlist
+
+responsive design
+
+
+Nice-to-Have
+
+planting calendar
+
+gardening journal
+
+bundle recommendations
+
+
+
+---
+
+10. SEO Requirements (VERY IMPORTANT)
+
+Traditional SEO
+
+Must include:
+
+semantic HTML
+
+optimized heading hierarchy
+
+metadata
+
+OpenGraph tags
+
+Twitter cards
+
+XML sitemap
+
+robots.txt
+
+schema markup
+
+image optimization
+
+lazy loading
+
+fast page speed
+
+
+
+---
+
+11. AI Search Optimization
+
+The site should be optimized for:
+
+ChatGPT search
+
+Google AI Overviews
+
+Perplexity
+
+Gemini
+
+Claude
+
+
+Content strategy should:
+
+answer questions clearly
+
+use FAQ sections
+
+explain gardening terms naturally
+
+include educational summaries
+
+use descriptive language
+
+
+Example: “Mint grows well in Karachi’s warm climate when given partial sunlight and regular watering.”
+
+
+---
+
+12. Target SEO Keywords
+
+Core Keywords
+
+buy seeds online Pakistan
+
+vegetable seeds Pakistan
+
+flower seeds Pakistan
+
+gardening Pakistan
+
+native plants Pakistan
+
+rare seeds Pakistan
+
+organic seeds Pakistan
+
+
+Long Tail Keywords
+
+best plants for Karachi weather
+
+beginner gardening Pakistan
+
+balcony gardening Karachi
+
+heat resistant plants Pakistan
+
+
+
+---
+
+13. Design Direction
+
+Style
+
+Blend:
+
+botanical illustration
+
+premium organic branding
+
+ecological storytelling
+
+modern ecommerce UI
+
+
+Avoid:
+
+overly corporate design
+
+neon startup aesthetics
+
+sterile minimalism
+
+
+
+---
+
+14. UI Style
+
+Use:
+
+rounded cards
+
+soft shadows
+
+organic shapes
+
+earthy gradients
+
+subtle animations
+
+nature-inspired textures
+
+
+
+---
+
+15. Homepage Hero
+
+Suggested Hero Text
+
+Option 1
+
+“Grow the Extraordinary.”
+
+Option 2
+
+“Seeds for Gardens That Matter.”
+
+Option 3
+
+“Plant Something Beautiful.”
+
+CTA Buttons:
+
+Shop Seeds
+
+Explore Plants
+
+Start Growing
+
+
+
+---
+
+16. Mobile Optimization
+
+Prioritize:
+
+mobile-first design
+
+fast loading
+
+optimized checkout
+
+sticky navigation
+
+thumb-friendly UI
+
+compressed assets
+
+
+
+---
+
+17. Performance Goals
+
+Target:
+
+Lighthouse score above 90
+
+fast page loading
+
+optimized assets
+
+responsive performance
+
+
+
+---
+
+18. Accessibility
+
+Must include:
+
+alt text
+
+readable contrast
+
+semantic structure
+
+keyboard accessibility
+
+screen reader compatibility
+
+
+
+---
+
+19. Future Features (DO NOT BUILD YET)
+
+1. Community Forum
+
+Future section for:
+
+gardening discussions
+
+seed sharing
+
+growing tips
+
+restoration discussions
+
+local gardening community
+
+
+Architecture should allow future expansion.
+
+
+---
+
+2. Native Karachi Integration
+
+Future ecosystem/restoration project integration.
+
+Potential future features:
+
+native species database
+
+restoration mapping
+
+ecological education
+
+citizen science submissions
+
+
+Only reserve scalable structure for this.
+
+
+---
+
+3. Plant Quiz System
+
+Future educational quiz feature.
+
+Potential uses:
+
+beginner gardening recommendations
+
+“What plant should you grow?”
+
+climate compatibility suggestions
+
+plant care guidance
+
+
+Do NOT implement yet.
+
+
+---
+
+20. Shopify Apps Recommended
+
+Judge.me Reviews
+
+Klaviyo
+
+TinyIMG SEO
+
+Shopify Inbox
+
+Wishlist App
+
+Bundle App
+
+
+
+---
+
+21. Tone of Voice
+
+The brand voice should feel:
+
+educational
+
+calm
+
+hopeful
+
+intelligent
+
+grounded
+
+ecological
+
+
+Avoid:
+
+aggressive marketing
+
+fake urgency
+
+excessive corporate language
+
+
+
+---
+
+22. Final Deliverables for Lovable
+
+Generate:
+
+fully responsive frontend
+
+Shopify integration structure
+
+reusable components
+
+SEO-ready architecture
+
+blog system
+
+ecommerce product templates
+
+scalable folder structure
+
+production-ready React + Tailwind code
+
+
+
+---
+
+23. Final Creative Direction
+
+Nayab Seeds should feel like:
+
+> “A modern ecological seed company focused on helping people grow beautiful, resilient gardens while reconnecting with nature.”
+
+
+
+The website should emotionally communicate:
+
+growth
+
+care
+
+biodiversity
+
+restoration
+
+warmth
+
+possibility
+
+ecological hope

